      "mode": "coop",
      "time": "15",
      "attribution": "Board layout by ArnoldSmith86. Released to public domain under CC0.\n\nImages are Noto Emoji, Material Symbols and Game-icons.net. See About for details.\n\nRules text by ArnoldSmith86 with formatting help by ChatGPT. Released to public domain under CC0.",
      "lastUpdate": 1774272861652,
      "skill": "",
      "description": "A cooperative dice-placement push-your-luck game where you try to finish food patterns efficiently before the cat advances too far.",
      "similarImage": "",
      "similarName": "Mmm!",
      "similarDesigner": "Reiner Knizia",
      "similarAwards": "2016 Kinderspiel des Jahres Nominee\n2016 JUGuinho Children Game of the Year Finalist\n2015 Spiel der Spiele Game of the Year Winner",
      "ruleText": "<h2>🎯 Objective</h2><p>Place dice on every space of the board before the cat arrives!&nbsp;🐈‍⬛</p><br><h2>⚙️ Setup</h2><p>To use the advanced board or start a new game, simply press&nbsp;<i class=\"richtextSymbol material-symbols\">restart_alt</i>.</p><br><h2>🎲 Turn</h2><ul><li><p>Roll <strong>3 dice</strong> 🎲🎲🎲&nbsp;by pressing&nbsp;<i class=\"richtextSymbol gameicons\"><img src=\"/i/game-icons.net/delapouite/rolling-dices.svg\"></i>.</p></li><li><p>Place <strong>one or more dice</strong> on matching spaces on the board.</p></li><li><p>Then either:</p><ul><li><p>Re-roll the remaining dice&nbsp;by pressing&nbsp;<i class=\"richtextSymbol gameicons\"><img src=\"/i/game-icons.net/delapouite/rolling-dices.svg\"></i>&nbsp;and repeat, or</p></li><li><p>Stop your turn.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>If you <strong>stop your turn</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Replace all placed dice with mouse tokens&nbsp;by pressing&nbsp;🐭<i class=\"richtextSymbol material-symbols\">arrow_forward</i>.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>If you <strong>roll but cannot place any dice</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Take all dice back from the board by pressing&nbsp;<i class=\"richtextSymbol material-symbols\">arrow_back</i><span>🎲.</span></p></li></ul></li><li><p>If <strong>no food area</strong><span><span> (e.g., 3 adjacent carrots 🥕🥕🥕) was completed this turn:</span></span></p><ul><li><p><span>Advance the cat&nbsp;</span><span>🐈‍⬛ one space on its track.</span><span>️</span></p></li></ul></li></ul><br><h2><span><span>🏁 End of the Game</span></span></h2><ul><li><p><strong><span><span>❌&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span>Lose</span></strong><span><span>: The cat reaches&nbsp;🍽️.</span></span></p></li><li><p><strong><span><span>✅&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span>Win</span></strong>: All board spaces are covered by&nbsp;<span><span>🐭.</span></span></p></li></ul><p><span><span>⭐ Challenge yourself: Try to win while leaving </span></span><strong>6 or more empty cat spaces</strong>!</p><br><h2><span><span>🔥 Difficulty Variant</span></span></h2><p data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">All dice placed during a single round must be in <strong>one row OR one column</strong>.</p>",
